        "title": "CARBINOX TROUBLESHOOTING GUIDE.",
        "content": "<p><strong>All Carbinox products are made with the highest quality standards to provide a positive experience to all our customers across the nation.</strong></p><p><strong>We’ve created this troubleshooting guide to provide solutions to anything you may be facing with your new smartwatch.</strong></p><p><strong>It’s imperative to understand how your new product works to get the most out of it.</strong></p>",
