        "title": "ABOUT TEXT MESSAGES:",
        "content": "<p><strong>What to do if notifications from WhatsApp or SMS are not being delivered on the watch?</strong></p><ul><li>Please make sure your phone IS NOT in silent mode.</li><li>Please make sure your watch IS NOT in silent mode.</li><li>Please make sure that \"Notifications\" on WhatsApp are turned on to receive them. This is through your phone settings.</li><li>Please make sure you included WhatsApp on the notification settings on the app Carbinox Pro.</li><li>Please make sure you don't have WhatsApp open in the computer.</li><li>Please make sure you have the \"Do not disturb\" feature turned on on your smartwatch.</li></ul>",
